[Follow Your Heart]

3
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:03,970
[Episode 8]

4
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:09,310
Fine.

5
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,450
We have plenty of time.

6
00:02:12,390 --> 00:02:13,789
Send the thief last night

7
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:15,580
back to the Jinwu Guards

8
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,620
by the end of the day.

9
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:23,229
Let's go!

10
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:30,950
Dismissed.

11
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,310
My lord,

12
00:02:40,810 --> 00:02:41,910
I only heard that Shang Bieli

13
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:43,570
once worked under Nan Jifeng.

14
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:44,329
I didn't know

15
00:02:44,329 --> 00:02:45,790
they were sworn brothers.

16
00:02:46,030 --> 00:02:47,230
That's not the point.

17
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:48,430
The point is

18
00:02:49,510 --> 00:02:51,070
it took Shang Bieli so little time

19
00:02:51,070 --> 00:02:52,870
to find out that we went to Heman.

20
00:02:53,110 --> 00:02:53,990
That means

21
00:02:54,510 --> 00:02:57,170
that batch of Zornia has arrived in the capital,

22
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,079
and

23
00:02:58,670 --> 00:03:00,550
the people who sent the Zornia to the capital

24
00:03:00,550 --> 00:03:01,590
already know

25
00:03:01,950 --> 00:03:03,590
the lord who appeared in Heman

26
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:04,300
was me.

27
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,090
It was indeed fast.

28
00:03:06,510 --> 00:03:08,070
I'm afraid His Majesty will soon

29
00:03:08,070 --> 00:03:08,750
know it.

30
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,000
They spread the news

31
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:15,630
because they wanted me to be scolded by His Majesty

32
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:17,860
so that they could stop my investigation.

33
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:18,540
So,

34
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:20,450
we must find that batch of Zornia

35
00:03:20,450 --> 00:03:21,990
and root out their contact in the capital

36
00:03:21,990 --> 00:03:24,080
as soon as possible.

37
00:03:24,770 --> 00:03:25,630
Only in this way

38
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:27,650
can we explain to His Majesty.

39
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:28,480
Understood.

40
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,280
Go invite Mr. Fu,

41
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:32,100
Mr. Shen,

42
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,800
and Mr. Wang

43
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:35,220
to a meeting at the meeting hall at 3 AM.

44
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:35,950
Yes.

45
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,860
[Prevent Wrongful Convictions and Don't Coddle Criminals]

46
00:03:46,950 --> 00:03:47,430
My lord,

47
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:48,670
everyone's here.

48
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,100
-My lord.
-My lord.

49
00:03:55,110 --> 00:03:56,070
Mr. Wang.

50
00:03:56,550 --> 00:03:57,350
Mr. Fu.

51
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,510
Mr. Shen.

52
00:03:58,829 --> 00:03:59,829
It's been a while.

53
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:01,110
How have you been?

54
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:06,890
This batch of Zornia was first transported by ship and then over land.

55
00:04:06,950 --> 00:04:07,950
It should be

56
00:04:08,579 --> 00:04:09,870
in the capital by now.

57
00:04:10,350 --> 00:04:11,210
Right, my lord.

58
00:04:11,550 --> 00:04:12,980
Not long after they took the Zornia out of Heman,

59
00:04:12,980 --> 00:04:15,120
they transferred it from the ship to a carriage.

60
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,390
They changed the carriage

61
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:17,550
every time they passed a checkpoint.

62
00:04:17,550 --> 00:04:18,900
After arriving at the posthouse outside the capital,

63
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:20,190
they designed a cover-up

64
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:21,310
by driving three carriages

65
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:23,370
into the capital at different times.

66
00:04:23,510 --> 00:04:24,550
Our men are trying to find out

67
00:04:24,550 --> 00:04:25,740
which carriage they put the Zornia in.

68
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:28,110
Perhaps there's Zornia in all three carriages.

69
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:28,670
My lord,

70
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,730
after we locate the Zornia,

71
00:04:30,740 --> 00:04:33,600
shall we seize it and arrest those men immediately?

72
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:34,910
Don't rush.

73
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:39,140
I deliberately let them take the Zornia out of Heman

74
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:40,590
to catch a big fish.

75
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,600
We just need to keep an eye on the bait

76
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:44,990
and see

77
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,550
who'll rise to it.

78
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,870
But the checkpoint through which the Zornia entered the capital

79
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:50,870
was controlled by the Jinwu Guards.

80
00:04:50,909 --> 00:04:52,610
If they had checked it thoroughly,

81
00:04:52,610 --> 00:04:53,390
the Zornia

82
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:55,310
wouldn't have entered the capital.

83
00:04:55,310 --> 00:04:56,909
Now that it's in the capital,

84
00:04:57,030 --> 00:04:57,960
the Jinwu Guards

85
00:04:58,030 --> 00:04:59,790
should be the first to be held accountable.

86
00:04:59,790 --> 00:05:01,990
At least they're guilty of negligence.

87
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:02,950
I'm afraid

88
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:05,150
the Jinwu Guards will give us a hard time

89
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,840
in order to shift the blame.

90
00:05:07,220 --> 00:05:09,430
They've already given us a lot of hard times!

91
00:05:09,430 --> 00:05:10,830
What Mr. Fu said is right.

92
00:05:12,030 --> 00:05:13,550
The Jinwu Guards failed to guard the city gate

93
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:15,410
and let Zornia enter the capital.

94
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:16,430
They

95
00:05:16,790 --> 00:05:18,300
can't get away with it.

96
00:05:18,670 --> 00:05:19,180
My lord,

97
00:05:19,690 --> 00:05:21,830
did Shang Bieli pick a fight here this morning

98
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,510
to give us a hint?

99
00:05:24,770 --> 00:05:25,360
My lord,

100
00:05:25,670 --> 00:05:27,200
I'm still a little worried.

101
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:28,590
It was a risky move

102
00:05:28,590 --> 00:05:30,670
to let them take the Zornia out of Heman.

103
00:05:30,670 --> 00:05:32,000
If anything goes wrong,

104
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,110
we'll be guilty

105
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:35,110
of leading others to commit a crime.

106
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:37,440
The jurisdiction given by His Majesty

107
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:39,210
has made others jealous of us.

108
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,550
If we get caught,

109
00:05:40,910 --> 00:05:42,630
it will cause a lot of trouble.

110
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,070
By then,

111
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:45,710
our mistake will be more serious

112
00:05:45,710 --> 00:05:47,230
than the Jinwu Guards'.

113
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:53,630
The moment I let the Zornia out of Heman,

114
00:05:53,990 --> 00:05:54,950
I knew

115
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,350
I must

116
00:05:57,590 --> 00:05:58,670
succeed.

117
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:04,270
Gentlemen,

118
00:06:05,230 --> 00:06:06,909
don't let this batch of Zornia

119
00:06:06,990 --> 00:06:07,990
go to market.

120
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:09,409
-Yes.
-Yes.

121
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:08,970
Since I started to shapeshift,

122
00:07:08,970 --> 00:07:10,500
I've been keeping records.

123
00:07:10,550 --> 00:07:11,350
But I still

124
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:12,750
haven't found a pattern.

125
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:19,910
Young Sir,

126
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:21,710
when I get to the capital,

127
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:22,830
I will find you.

128
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:24,540
No matter what you look like by then,

129
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:25,550
I'll accept it.

130
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,080
I'll protect you.

131
00:07:45,450 --> 00:07:48,020
[No. 4 Taiping Alley, Nanhua District]

132
00:08:01,909 --> 00:08:02,970
Aren't you coming?

133
00:08:03,090 --> 00:08:04,490
What are you waiting for?

134
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:05,470
Well,

135
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:08,350
how did you see through my disguise again?

136
00:08:08,350 --> 00:08:08,710
My lord,

137
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:10,070
you're so smart.

138
00:08:10,470 --> 00:08:11,750
It's not because I'm smart,

139
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:13,150
but because you didn't pay enough attention to detail.

140
00:08:13,150 --> 00:08:13,909
Right.

141
00:08:14,050 --> 00:08:15,690
My lord, you're sharp.

142
00:08:17,150 --> 00:08:17,810
But how did you

143
00:08:17,810 --> 00:08:19,170
see through my disguise this time?

144
00:08:19,170 --> 00:08:21,350
Last time, you said it was from my smell.

145
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:22,530
But this time, before I came out,

146
00:08:22,530 --> 00:08:23,240
I burned incense,

147
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,230
and I'm wearing a sachet.

148
00:08:24,230 --> 00:08:25,550
It can cover my smell.

149
00:08:26,350 --> 00:08:28,350
What betrayed you was not your smell

150
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:29,500
but your hand.

151
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:30,800
My hand?

152
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:34,330
What was wrong with my hand?

153
00:08:34,330 --> 00:08:35,850
The way you waved your fan

154
00:08:36,070 --> 00:08:37,310
seemed very stiff.

155
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:39,180
Obviously, you don't use fans very often.

156
00:08:39,180 --> 00:08:39,870
Besides,

157
00:08:40,590 --> 00:08:42,850
although you're dressed like a playboy,

158
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:45,350
there are calluses on your hand,

159
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,860
which clearly shows you've practiced martial arts

160
00:08:46,860 --> 00:08:47,580
for years.

161
00:08:49,309 --> 00:08:50,370
Most importantly,

162
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:52,830
playboys usually

163
00:08:53,190 --> 00:08:54,960
sleep late.

164
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,299
I was careless.

165
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:58,960
I'll be more careful next time.

166
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,630
Let's go.

167
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:00,960
My lord, please.

168
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:26,870
I was away for two months,

169
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,930
and Daimao doesn't recognize me now.

170
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:31,030
You never confuse them?

171
00:09:35,170 --> 00:09:36,740
Linglong has gained weight,

172
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:38,070
and Shuijing has lost weight.

173
00:09:38,070 --> 00:09:39,800
Daimao and Huanpei had a fight.

174
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:41,800
Their tails

175
00:09:41,830 --> 00:09:42,870
got injured.

176
00:09:43,230 --> 00:09:44,320
The rest are fine.

177
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,950
The pigeons

178
00:09:47,950 --> 00:09:48,790
look so alike,

179
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:50,650
yet you can tell one from another.

180
00:09:50,950 --> 00:09:53,010
How come you can't recognize people?

181
00:09:59,110 --> 00:10:00,970
Because everyone has many faces,

182
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:03,120
and they may change it anytime.

183
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,070
That's right.

184
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:05,240
Most people

185
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:07,060
act in their self-interest.

186
00:10:07,070 --> 00:10:08,480
They tend to change their attitude anytime.

187
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,860
The only forthright, sincere person

188
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:11,430
I've seen over the years

189
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:13,250
is the Poison Girl.

190
00:10:17,430 --> 00:10:18,790
Her name is Yan Nanxing.

191
00:10:19,510 --> 00:10:20,510
Okay.

192
00:10:20,780 --> 00:10:21,590
Yan Nanxing.

193
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:22,950
My lord,

194
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:24,790
haven't you ever thought about

195
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:25,950
looking for Ms. Yan?

196
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:30,510
Where

197
00:10:31,100 --> 00:10:32,160
are you going next?

198
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:36,230
Perhaps

199
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:39,870
I'll go to my mother

200
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:41,480
or

201
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:43,570
somewhere I've never been to.

202
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,060
If...

203
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:48,150
If I run into trouble,

204
00:10:48,310 --> 00:10:50,170
I'll go to the capital to find you.

205
00:10:55,470 --> 00:10:57,070
She didn't commit a crime.

206
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:58,910
Why should I look for her?

207
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:00,310
My lord,

208
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:01,520
you know

209
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:02,670
I didn't mean that.

210
00:11:02,950 --> 00:11:04,080
Now that she's gone,

211
00:11:04,290 --> 00:11:05,470
aren't you worried about her?

212
00:11:05,470 --> 00:11:06,530
Don't you miss her?

213
00:11:11,990 --> 00:11:12,910
Have you found out

214
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,370
where the goods from Heman

215
00:11:14,470 --> 00:11:15,270
are?

216
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:16,550
My lord,

217
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:19,040
the goods were taken to Fanhou Street.

218
00:11:19,190 --> 00:11:20,270
Fanhou Street?

219
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:22,390
The Ghost Market?

220
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,190
That's right.

221
00:11:26,190 --> 00:11:27,550
No wonder

222
00:11:27,590 --> 00:11:29,050
we didn't find any traces.

223
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:32,200
Turns out the Zornia was taken into the Ghost Market.

224
00:11:33,030 --> 00:11:35,490
Which store in the market did they take it to?

225
00:11:36,670 --> 00:11:37,400
We lost them.

226
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:39,590
You lost them?

227
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:41,830
Don't worry, my lord.

228
00:11:41,830 --> 00:11:43,870
The Ghost Market's road network is complex.

229
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:44,470
Our men

230
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:46,110
lost them at the last moment.

231
00:11:46,390 --> 00:11:48,390
The goods must be still in the market.

232
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,870
I've sent spies there.

233
00:11:50,170 --> 00:11:51,310
If anything happens,

234
00:11:51,310 --> 00:11:53,110
they'll report it immediately.

235
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:55,880
They were in such a hurry

236
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:58,890
to transport the Zornia from Heman to the capital.

237
00:11:58,890 --> 00:11:59,940
This batch of Zornia won't be kept

238
00:11:59,940 --> 00:12:01,390
in the Ghost Market for long

239
00:12:01,390 --> 00:12:03,350
and will soon go to market.

240
00:12:08,190 --> 00:12:08,910
It seems

241
00:12:09,590 --> 00:12:10,630
the big fish

242
00:12:10,990 --> 00:12:12,390
is about to take the bait.

243
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,350
Don't worry, my lord.

244
00:12:14,350 --> 00:12:16,010
Our men are watching closely.

245
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:19,310
Didn't you say there were three carriages?

246
00:12:19,310 --> 00:12:20,550
What about the other two?

247
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:21,950
We've checked the other two.

248
00:12:21,950 --> 00:12:23,270
One was hired by them randomly,

249
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:24,470
and there was nothing wrong with it.

250
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:26,160
The woman from Heman

251
00:12:26,190 --> 00:12:27,610
was sitting in the other carriage.

252
00:12:27,610 --> 00:12:29,070
Our men are following her.

253
00:12:30,450 --> 00:12:31,070
My lord,

254
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:32,690
the woman who transported the Zornia from Heman to the capital

255
00:12:32,690 --> 00:12:33,790
found out we were after her.

256
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:35,070
She went to Twelve Music House

257
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:37,470
and are now surrounded by the Jinwu Guards.

258
00:12:39,420 --> 00:12:42,280
[Twelve Music House]

259
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:57,310
Move.

260
00:12:57,310 --> 00:12:57,710
Make way.

261
00:12:57,710 --> 00:12:59,230
Get out of the way.

262
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:00,960
The officers are here.

263
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:01,390
Yes.

264
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:11,510
Jiang Xinbai,

265
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:14,100
I didn't mean to do your job.

266
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:15,910
She came in herself.

267
00:13:16,910 --> 00:13:18,270
I can't let her kill someone

268
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,070
under my nose.

269
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:22,520
The Inspection Office will take over now.

270
00:13:22,710 --> 00:13:24,940
Please take your Jinwu Guards away.

271
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,550
Do you think we're

272
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:32,020
entertainers at Twelve Music House

273
00:13:33,010 --> 00:13:34,120
who come and go

274
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,990
as you wish?

275
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:37,390
Let me go,

276
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:38,550
or

277
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:39,590
I'll cut her neck.

278
00:13:42,190 --> 00:13:42,950
Mr. Shang,

279
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:45,470
we can talk about

280
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:47,200
our personal grudge later.

281
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:48,310
Now,

282
00:13:48,990 --> 00:13:51,630
please take your Jinwu Guards away.

283
00:13:52,110 --> 00:13:53,910
You don't know how to treat girls gently.

284
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:55,630
I'm afraid once you do something,

285
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:56,870
both girls

286
00:13:57,230 --> 00:13:58,030
will die.

287
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:27,750
Why did you kill her?

288
00:14:30,670 --> 00:14:32,070
I killed the suspect

289
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:33,930
to protect the victim.

290
00:14:34,430 --> 00:14:35,290
Was that wrong?

291
00:14:38,510 --> 00:14:39,770
