893
00:39:42,630 --> 00:39:43,990
784.

894
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:48,110
You're amazing!

895
00:39:50,540 --> 00:39:52,310
Let's go down and have a look.

896
00:39:53,230 --> 00:39:53,870
My lord,

897
00:39:54,150 --> 00:39:55,670
