898
00:39:55,670 --> 00:39:56,390
Shall we...

899
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:57,800
Shake her off.

900
00:40:10,450 --> 00:40:12,980
Why did Jiang Xinbai come to the Ghost Market?

901
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:15,370
Let me see

902
00:40:15,870 --> 00:40:17,110
